reviewText: The tape is jumping a it
this is a awesome show and this is the best first 2 episodes of the season. if you have not seen this video then I recommend you do

In the original episodes, the kids searched for the crystals while the Alien Rangers took their place on Earth, and there was a before-credits preview *for* Zeo, and those previews were never, *ever* re-aired... and none of that is on this tape. This video cuts everything but the Ranger kids searching for the crystals. So... get it for the Zeo Crystal quest, but don't buy it expecting the whole episodes. I did and was very disappointed.
This video is about when the Power Rangers travel around the world looking for the zeo subcrystals. But don't worry. While the Power Rangers are gone, the alien rangers will protect Angel Grove.
The Rangers embark on a quest to restore there powers and these powers are even better than the last.  With a great plot and awsome effects this movie is definatly the video to buy.
